不是凯茜·杜兰特
It's not Cathy Durant.

727
00:48:27,100 --> 00:48:28,160
我们能确定吗
Are we sure?

728
00:48:28,520 --> 00:48:29,860
她争取了豁免权
She negotiated immunity.

729
00:48:29,870 --> 00:48:30,620
她作证时
And she's going on record

730
00:48:30,630 --> 00:48:32,860
将公开她知道的一切
with everything she knows when she testifies.

731
00:48:39,380 --> 00:48:41,020
我们知道是谁吗
Do we have any idea?

732
00:48:41,900 --> 00:48:42,790
不知道
No.

733
00:48:49,270 --> 00:48:50,090
好
Good.

734
00:48:50,590 --> 00:48:51,660
谢谢
Thanks.

